	  <concept id="i1076423"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">41.501</ph> Solicitation provision and contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2448e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2459e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Because the terms and conditions under which utility suppliers furnish service may vary from area to area, the differences may influence the terms and conditions appropriate to a particular utility’s contracting situation. To accommodate requirements that are peculiar to the contracting situation, this section prescribes provisions and clauses on a “substantially the same as” basis (see <xref href="FAR-i1064507.dita#i1064507"
                        base="i1064507"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.101</xref>) which permits the contracting officer to prepare and utilize variations of the prescribed provision and clauses in accordance with agency procedures.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2459e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert in solicitations for utility services a provision substantially the same as the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1047820.dita#i1047820"
                        base="i1047820"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.241-1</xref>, Electric Service Territory Compliance Representation, when proposals from alternative electric suppliers are sought.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2459e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert in solicitations and contracts for utility services clauses substantially the same as the clauses at-</p>
					          <ol id="d2448e47" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047831.dita#i1047831"
                              base="i1047831"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-2</xref>, Order of Precedence-Utilities;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e63" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047840.dita#i1047840"
                              base="i1047840"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-3</xref>, Scope and Duration of Contract;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e75" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047852.dita#i1047852"
                              base="i1047852"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-4</xref>, Change in Class of Service;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e87" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047862.dita#i1047862"
                              base="i1047862"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-5</xref>, Contractor’s Facilities; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e99" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047874.dita#i1047874"
                              base="i1047874"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-6</xref>, Service Provisions.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2459e113" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert clauses substantially the same as the clauses listed below in solicitations and contracts under the prescribed conditions-</p>
					          <ol id="d2448e119" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047891.dita#i1047891"
                              base="i1047891"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-7</xref>, Change in Rates or Terms and Conditions of Service for Regulated Services, when the utility services are subject to a regulatory body. (Except for GSA areawide contracts, the contracting officer shall insert in the blank space provided in the clause the name of the contracting officer. For GSA areawide contracts, the contracting officer shall insert the following: “GSA and each areawide customer with annual billings that exceed $250,000”).</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e135" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047907.dita#i1047907"
                              base="i1047907"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-8</xref>, Change in Rates or Terms and Conditions of Service for Unregulated Services, when the utility services are not subject to a regulatory body.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e147" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047920.dita#i1047920"
                              base="i1047920"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-9</xref>, Connection Charge, when a refundable connection charge is required to be paid by the Government to compensate the contractor for furnishing additional facilities necessary to supply service. (Use AlternateI to the clause if a nonrefundable charge is to be paid. When conditions require the incorporation of a nonrecurring, nonrefundable service charge or a termination liability, see paragraphs(d)(6) and (d)(4) of this section).</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e159" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047944.dita#i1047944"
                              base="i1047944"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-10</xref>, Termination Liability, when payment is to be made to the contractor upon termination of service in conjunction with or in lieu of a connection charge upon completion of the facilities.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e171" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047958.dita#i1047958"
                              base="i1047958"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-11</xref>, Multiple Service Locations (as defined in <xref href="FAR-i1076819.dita#i1076819"
                              base="i1076819"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">41.101</xref>), when providing for possible alternative service locations, except under areawide contracts, is required.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e187" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047968.dita#i1047968"
                              base="i1047968"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-12</xref>, Nonrefundable, Nonrecurring Service Charge, when the Government is required to pay a nonrefundable, nonrecurring membership fee, a charge for initiation of service, or a contribution for the cost of facilities construction. The Government may provide for inclusion of such agreed amount or fee as a part of the connection charge, a part of the initial payment for services, or as periodic payments to fulfill the Government’s obligation.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2459e199" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(7)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <xref href="FAR-i1047977.dita#i1047977"
                              base="i1047977"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.241-13</xref>, Capital Credits, when the Federal Government is a member of a cooperative and is entitled to capital credits, consistent with the bylaws and governing documents of the cooperative.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2459e213" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Depending on the conditions that are appropriate for each acquisition, the contracting officer shall also insert in solicitations and contracts for utility services the provisions and clauses prescribed elsewhere in the FAR.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
